    <item>
      <title>英国保守党誓言撤销伦敦清洁空气区扩张计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/uk-s-tories-vow-to-reverse-london-clean-air-zone-expansion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[执政的保守党表示，如果他们在下个月的大选中继续执政，他们将撤销伦敦清洁空气区的扩张计划——该计划要求对污染车辆征收费用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/uk-s-tories-vow-to-reverse-london-clean-air-zone-expansion</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 21:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工党计划改革英国商业税率以扶持小企业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/keir-starmer-s-labour-plans-to-overhaul-uk-business-rates-to-help-small-firms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基尔·史塔默 (Keir Starmer) 领导的工党誓言，如果在下个月的大选中获得通过，将通过改革英国营业税（即商业场所的房产税）来“为商业街和在线零售商提供公平的竞争环境”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/keir-starmer-s-labour-plans-to-overhaul-uk-business-rates-to-help-small-firms</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 21:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
